Introduction

Kim Ryeo Wook is a South Korean singer, songwriter, DJ, TV personality and musical actor under Label SJ, a subsidary of SM Entertainment. He is best known for being the main vocalist of the boy group Super Junior and its sub-units Super Junior K.R.Y and Super Junior M.
